<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/usstock/c/2020-12-03/doc-iiznezxs5008949.shtml">必胜客创始人弗兰克・卡尼去世</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1384101" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>界面消息，美国披萨连锁品牌必胜客（Pizzahut）创始人之一弗兰克・卡尼（Frank Carney）于当地时间 12 月 2 日凌晨 4 点 30 分因肺炎病逝，享年 82 岁。卡尼近日才从新冠肺炎中康复，他已身患阿兹海默症十多年。</p>
<p>弗兰克与哥哥于 1958 年在堪萨斯州威奇托市，开始携手创建必胜客。</p>
<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/tDG_i62Fx21svAqCj74v_g">元气森林月销售额一度破 4 亿</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1384102" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/yuanqi.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/yuanqi.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/yuanqi-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/yuanqi-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/yuanqi-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>食品板援引业内人士消息称，虽然疫情让国内企业「很受伤」，但元气森林今年的月销售额一度破 4 亿元，完成 25 亿的年销售目标问题不大。</p>
<p>而就在前不久召开的经销商大会上，元气森林也透露了 2021 年的线下渠道销售目标，从今年的 21 亿提升到明年的 75 亿。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.com/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release">奥利奥和 Lady Gaga 推出合作款饼干</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1384103" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release-cookie.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release-cookie.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release-cookie-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release-cookie-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/lady-gaga-oreo-chromatica-cookie-release-cookie-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>奥利奥和 Lady Gaga 合作推出特别版奥利奥饼干。该新品设计灵感来自 Lady Gaga 的专辑《Chromatica》，饼干颜色为粉红色，并印有对应图案，饼干的夹心奶油也换成了绿色。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release">万代推出《新世纪福音战士》电子宠物机</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1384104" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release-1.jpg" alt="" width="1400" height="933" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release-1.jpg 1400w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/premium-bandai-new-neon-genesis-evangelion-tamagotchi-release-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，万代推出《新世纪福音战士》主题电子宠物机，玩家可以从中育成主要角色：渚薰、真希波和绫波零。</p>
<p>该系列现在已经可在 Premium BANDAI 官网预订，定价为 2530 日元（约人民币 160 元）。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%2300%E5%90%8E%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E7%9C%BC%E7%BA%BF%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F4%E5%80%8D%23&amp;Refer=top">00 后男生眼线消费增速是女生 4 倍</a></h4>
<p>统计数据显示，2020 年 00 后男生彩妆消费增速已远超 00 后女生。</p>
<p>其中，00 后男生购买粉底液的增速是女生的 2 倍，眼线的增速是女生的 4 倍。最爱买眼妆产品的是广东男生，排名前三的城市分别是 ：深圳、揭阳、汕头。</p>
<p>网友：「感觉很多男孩已经达到化妆的最高境界，一般人看不出他们化了妆。」「增速快不代表总量多啊，女生原本消费基数就很大。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357583" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>一起看个展：《幻景：当代艺术与增强现实》</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383844" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/79c64dfe618c4a858a4364bb6fc623c1.gif" alt="" width="360" height="640" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/1f4cd.png" alt="📍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />  UCCA 尤伦斯当代艺术中心 · 北京</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/231b.png" alt="⌛" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />  2020.11.28 &#8211; 2021.2.10</strong></p>
<p>UCCA 和 Acute Art 合作打造了这次 AR 艺术特展，带来了妮娜・香奈尔・阿布尼、达伦・巴德、曹斐、奥拉维尔・埃利亚松、KAWS 和阿丽莎・柯维德的作品。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383845" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a41a1755d7d94d5787959bdbf78bdc62.jpeg" alt="" width="1080" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a41a1755d7d94d5787959bdbf78bdc62.jpeg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a41a1755d7d94d5787959bdbf78bdc62-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a41a1755d7d94d5787959bdbf78bdc62-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a41a1755d7d94d5787959bdbf78bdc62-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p>本次展出的都是 AR 作品，需结合智能手机观看。UCCA 馆内也为观众免费提供 iPhone 12 系列手机，以方便所有参观者体验本次展出的 AR 艺术作品。</p>
